data.description: You won't want to miss this private oasis! This home is great for outdoor lovers with a new (2022) 10 x 16 shed (with electrical), a beautiful deck, and a completely fenced-in backyard, including a firepit! Inside, the primary bedroom boasts a large walk-in closet, a spacious bathroom with a skylight, a jetted tub, and a walk-in tile shower. This home has been meticulously cared for, evident in the well-maintained landscaping, sealed crawl space with a dehumidifier, new carpet, and new back roof. The home has an open kitchen with a seated bar area, granite, stainless steel appliances, and a separate eat-in area with bar.
